OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry, warm and sunny start to
OL,6,Fthe day. Turning even hotter as the
OL,7,Fday goes on with extreme heat
OL,8,Fcontinuing along with high humidity.
OL,9,FPerhaps some high cloud moving in at
OL,10,Ftimes in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying very warm and humid
OL,13,Fovernight. Dry for most but elevated
OL,14,Fthunderstorm moving into the south.
OL,15,FCould turn gusty for some with the odd
OL,16,Frumble of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
