OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny early morning
OL,6,Fthunderstorms will move northward.
OL,7,FAnother very hot day to come as
OL,8,Fhumidity levels remain high. Very
OL,9,Flittle cloud to start but could see
OL,10,Fsome more later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,13,Fhot into the weekend, but temperatures
OL,14,Fslowly coming down by Sunday. Dry for
OL,15,Fmany but some spots of rain and
OL,16,Fshowers developing into the new week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
